name:                marquise-haskell
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            libmarquise haskell bindings
-- description:         
homepage:            github
license:             BSD3
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Anchor Hosting
maintainer:          pingu@anchor.net.au
